SmartHER Dispatch
-----------------

SmartHER News Reader & Anchorage resident Tarryn describes the scary moments when a 7.0 magnitude earthquake shook Alaska on Friday.

[Watch Now](https://www.youtube.com/embed/E5tM5aUmsbI?enablejsapi=1&autoplay=1&rel=0)

card_10.cardText:
Since the earthquake struck on Friday, more than 1400 aftershocks have been recorded. Alaska has the most earthquakes of any region.

[view sources](https://smarthernews.com/18-12-04-alaska-earthquake/)
